<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AI Stylist - BarberLux</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="page-wrapper">
        <%- include('partials/sidebar', { activePage: 'ai-stylist', user: user }) %>

        <!-- Main Content -->
        <main class="main-content d-flex flex-column">
            <div class="container-fluid flex-grow-1 d-flex flex-column">
                <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-4">
                    <h1>AI Stylist</h1>
                    <div id="quota-info" class="text-white-50"></div>
                </div>

                <!-- Subscription Call-to-Action -->
                <div id="subscribe-cta" class="alert alert-warning text-center" style="display: none;">
                    <h4 class="alert-heading">Kuota Habis!</h4>
                    <p>Kuota gratis Anda untuk bertanya pada AI Stylist telah habis. Lanjutkan dengan berlangganan hanya Rp 50.000/bulan untuk akses tanpa batas.</p>
                    <hr>
                    <button id="subscribe-btn" class="btn btn-primary fw-bold">Langganan Sekarang</button>
                </div>

                <div class="card flex-grow-1">
                    <div class="card-body d-flex flex-column p-0">
                        <!-- Chat Window -->
                        <div id="chat-window" class="chat-window flex-grow-1 p-3">
                            <div class="chat-message ai-message">
                                <div class="message-bubble">Halo! Saya AI Stylist dari BarberLux. Bingung mau potong rambut model apa? Tanyakan saja pada saya! Contoh: "Rekomendasi gaya rambut untuk wajah bulat"<div class="">
                                    <br>
                                </div>"Atau masukkan foto kamu yang jelas saya akan bantu rekomendasikan gaya rambut yang cocok untukmu.</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Chat Input -->
                        <div class="chat-input-area p-3 border-top" style="border-color: var(--bs-border-color) !important;">
                            <!-- Image preview area -->
                            <div id="image-preview-container" class="mb-2" style="display: none;">
                                <img id="image-preview" src="#" alt="Image Preview" />
                                <button type="button" id="remove-image-btn" class="btn-close btn-close-white"></button>
                            </div>
                            <form id="chat-form" class="d-flex gap-2">
                                <!-- Hidden file input -->
                                <input type="file" id="image-upload" name="faceImage" accept="image/*" style="display: none;">
                                <!-- Visible upload button -->
                                <button type="button" id="upload-btn" class="btn btn-secondary flex-shrink-0"><i class="bi bi-paperclip"></i></button>
                                <input type="text" id="chat-input" class="form-control" placeholder="Ketik pesan atau unggah gambar..." autocomplete="off">
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">
                                    <i class="bi bi-arrow-up"></i>
                                </button>
                            </form>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </main>
    </div>

    <!-- Midtrans Snap.js -->
    <script type="text/javascript" src="https://app.sandbox.midtrans.com/snap/snap.js" data-client-key="<%= midtransClientKey %>"></script>
    <!-- Library untuk mengubah Markdown menjadi HTML (dimuat dari CDN) -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/marked/marked.min.js"></script>
    <!-- Script khusus untuk halaman chat -->
    <script src="/js/chat.js"></script>
</body>
</html>